                <p>Thinkers. Doers. Scholars. Problem solvers. Visionaries.&nbsp;Meet some of the faculty, staff, and students who will shape your iSchool experience.</p>

<p>Our faculty advance the field through their forward-thinking ideas and research. Our staff provide top-notch student programs and services. Our alumni serve in leadership roles around the globe,&nbsp;mentor our students, and give generously of their time and resources to support the School. Our students demonstrate intelligence, creativity, and a passion to contribute to improving their communities.</p>

<p>Our people change the world through innovation and expertise—embracing&nbsp;a broad range of intellectual practices while furthering our School's ethic of service, empowerment, and social benefit.</p>

